entries.femaleVariant: Hm, you tell me. You're the ones they chose for that BD gig.
Jesus... Would it kill you to show a little empathy for once? I'm worried about him.
Yeah, poor guy. Made more in a week than I do in a whole month.
Thing is... I dunno if the scratch was worth it.
During the last sesh, they even aimed a gun at me. That wasn't in the script!
Him they cuffed, gagged... And they threatened to kill him.
